snippet.description: If you're not opting for a smartphone and you can look past its dated design, the Samsung Gravity Q is your best choice for a T-Mobile keyboard phone.

snippet.title: LG Envoy II (U.S. Cellular)
snippet.description: With its low-end specs and mediocre camera, the Envoy II isn't worth buying -- especially since the Samsung Chrono 2 comes in at a cheaper contract price.

snippet.title: Thunderspace for iPhone
snippet.description: Though it's a niche product, Thunderspace is a worthwhile download, with realistic-sounding storms that make for a relaxing experience.

snippet.title: Harman Kardon Soho-I
